00:52:49,440 --> 00:52:58,321
So Thart says that just the desire to be a free and vulnerable detached observer is sadistic.

663
00:52:58,321 --> 00:53:10,880
And that means, of course, that not only does Yvonne have his nice collection of newspaper clippings, but he has his job writing for the newspaper as the eyewitness, the detached observer.

664
00:53:10,880 --> 00:53:19,721
So, at all the levels, from really sort of dirty sadism to kind of very refined sadism, he's a sadist.

