00:53:20,681 --> 00:53:28,281
Later, you'll find Yvonne asking about the tortures in hell with great eagerness and interest.

666
00:53:28,281 --> 00:53:33,480
Because in the end, I guess every sadist must be a masochist, and the masochist must be a sadist somehow.

667
00:53:33,480 --> 00:53:35,481
I don't really know how to work it out.

