00:55:33,040 --> 00:55:40,161
Dostoevsky calls Yvonne the educated one before he has a name for him and the murderer.

680
00:55:40,161 --> 00:55:45,600
And that's to remember that the guy, the one who wants to play the angel, plays the beast.

681
00:55:45,601 --> 00:55:49,280
It's all part of the same dark story.

682
00:55:49,601 --> 00:55:52,161
So, what's the right thing to think?

683
00:55:52,480 --> 00:55:55,281
Well, first, Yvonne is not a spectator.

684
00:55:55,281 --> 00:55:56,400
He's not an eyewitness.

685
00:55:56,400 --> 00:55:57,520
He's a participant.

686
00:55:57,520 --> 00:55:58,720
He's part of the problem.

687
00:55:58,721 --> 00:56:00,321
He is guilty.

688
00:56:00,880 --> 00:56:04,241
And now the question is, and so we can't give back the ticket.

689
00:56:04,241 --> 00:56:11,360
So now comes the people over in this corner who asked and already had good ideas about what to do.

690
00:56:11,360 --> 00:56:12,160
There are two things.

691
00:56:12,161 --> 00:56:15,601
I mean, one is to discover Yvonne's argument is wrong.

692
00:56:15,601 --> 00:56:27,040
And the other one is to worry about, well, what are you supposed to do when you're enmeshed in a world in which there is evil in suffering innocent children, even if you're not sadistic?

693
00:56:27,360 --> 00:56:29,360
That's just Yvonne's problem.

694
00:56:29,360 --> 00:56:33,601
What are you supposed to do about living in that sort of world?

695
00:56:33,601 --> 00:56:41,920
So now we go to the person who has the most extreme opposite view of Yvonne from Yvonne's.

696
00:56:41,920 --> 00:56:43,200
Do you recognize that?

697
00:56:43,201 --> 00:56:44,321
Have you got far enough?

698
00:56:44,681 --> 00:56:45,800
I don't know.

699
00:56:47,161 --> 00:56:52,441
Who worries about the guilt of, who worries about being guilty for all the suffering?

700
00:56:52,440 --> 00:56:57,481
Well, maybe you haven't got to 184, though you should be getting there quickly.

701
00:56:57,480 --> 00:56:58,920
But it's Zosima.

702
00:56:58,920 --> 00:57:02,600
Zosima is the absolute opposite of Yvonne's story.

703
00:57:02,601 --> 00:57:15,561
Instead of claiming, like Yvonne, that he has no guilt, that he rejects the world because everybody else is guilty, Father Zosima claims that he's guilty for all the evil in the world.

704
00:57:15,560 --> 00:57:17,081
184.

705
00:57:17,641 --> 00:57:18,201
You should be...

706
00:57:18,520 --> 00:57:19,000
How far?

