01:01:08,201 --> 01:01:12,281
It's not the actual people who have actual problems.

747
01:01:12,440 --> 01:01:17,880
He does sort of treat people who come to the monastery like a kind of therapist.

748
01:01:17,880 --> 01:01:19,321
He does something.

749
01:01:19,321 --> 01:01:28,040
But he certainly doesn't deal with or have any sort of sensible relation to all the suffering in the world.

750
01:01:28,040 --> 01:01:34,121
Just to say that he feels guilty of it, he wants the whole world to forgive him, just isn't going to get anywhere.

751
01:01:34,121 --> 01:01:35,560
So let me see now.

