01:01:55,721 --> 01:02:00,721
Well, you see, in a way, Zosima thinks that he's everybody's keeper.

758
01:01:59,000 --> 01:02:02,000
Everybody's his brother.

759
01:02:02,321 --> 01:02:08,321
And that's just unrealistic and has no, isn't a way you can sensibly live.

760
01:02:08,960 --> 01:02:16,880
And it turns out that, of course, Yvonne says, just what you expect him to say, that he's nobody's keeper.

761
01:02:16,880 --> 01:02:18,880
He doesn't feel responsible for anything.

762
01:02:18,880 --> 01:02:20,241
He's going to leave.

763
01:02:20,241 --> 01:02:22,241
He's not involved.

764
01:02:22,241 --> 01:02:35,040
And the funny thing is, you begin to see Smerzhyakov as a copy of Yvonne on 255 when talking about Dmitri about two-thirds down, Smerdhyakov says, how should I know about Dmitry?

