01:06:43,440 --> 01:06:49,121
Because the next thing that comes up is that Christ is the one who should take on all the sorrows of the world.

825
01:06:49,121 --> 01:06:49,920
Let's go there.

826
01:06:50,161 --> 01:06:52,321
That's exactly where we're supposed to be.

827
01:06:52,321 --> 01:06:55,761
You're amazingly tuned in.

