01:06:55,761 --> 01:07:03,360
So Alyasha makes the move that he shouldn't make.

829
01:07:03,360 --> 01:07:19,241
He's now been so upset and confused by Yvonne that he asks whether somebody shouldn't, so to speak, take on the guilt and be able to give forgiveness.

830
01:07:21,161 --> 01:07:24,360
But it can't be the people in the monastery.

831
01:07:24,360 --> 01:07:26,520
And we can add that it would be blasphemous.

832
01:07:26,520 --> 01:07:27,640
He doesn't say that here.

